title: Expenditure on beer in the United Kingdom 2005 to 2018
summary: In general Expenditure in million GBP has rose over the Year.
Expenditure in million GBP is slightly increasing from 2012 to 2013, and lastly roughly constant from 2013 to 2015.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2012 and 2013.
The highest Expenditure in million GBP, of value 4573.0 was reached at Year 2014
The lowest Expenditure in million GBP, of value 4188.0 was reported at Year 2012
